<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="133">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="133">The species epithet is named in honor of Ms. Jiang-Hai He, a local staff in Huanglian Shan National Nature Reserve, who has worked there for almost 30 years and made a big contribution to the knowledge of biodiversity of this nature reserve, and is also the discoverer of this new species.</paragraph>
